        <li>(a) an application for a licence to abstract water to prevent interference with any mining, quarrying or engineering operations (whether underground or surface) or to prevent damage to works resulting front any such operations is first applied for as a result of the coining into force of this section (which has had the effect of making the above abstraction an abstraction to which the restriction in section 24 applies); and</li>
