        <q>Page 12, line 38, after "made" insert "prior to the commencement of this section</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0646P0-05295'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0646P0_20030401_GCR_142' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
